    {
      "id": "bottom-question",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 114,
      "y": 234,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 60,
      "text": "The debate: Critics want AI to move RIGHT on this spectrum (more friction = more personality).\nBut users keep pulling it LEFT (more helpful = more useful).\nMaybe \"personality\" isn't on this axis at all?",
